  "title": "⭐️Brand Engagement Lead (Entry Level)⭐️",
  "description": "<p><strong>Start Strong. Grow Confidently.</strong></p><p>At <strong>DASH</strong>, we believe every great career starts with the right foundation. We partner with leading brands across essential services, technology, lifestyle and non-profit sectors! We’re looking for enthusiastic individuals ready to learn, grow, and succeed— no prior sales experience required.</p><p>If you have the right attitude and a willingness to learn, we’ll provide the skills, mentorship, and support to help you thrive.</p><p><strong>The Role:</strong></p><ul><li>Connect with customers face-to-face, sharing solutions that make their lives easier 🎋<br /><br /></li><li>Develop essential communication and presentation skills with hands-on experience⚒️<br /><br /></li><li>Learn and apply ethical, structured sales strategies📊<br /><br /></li><li>Progress into leadership opportunities as you gain confidence and results💡<br /><br /></li></ul><p><strong>You Get:</strong></p><ul><li>Comprehensive 1-on-1 Training from industry professionals🫱🏼‍🫲🏻<br /><br /></li><li>Step-by-step skill development for personal and career growth👣<br /><br /></li><li>A positive, supportive team that celebrates every milestone with you🎉<br /><br /></li><li>Performance-based promotions—your results set the pace📈<br /><br /></li><li>Opportunities for local and overseas exposure✈️✨<br /><br /></li></ul><p><strong>We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li>Open-minded individuals eager to learn and improve🧠<br /><br /></li><li>Great listeners who enjoy connecting with people👂🏼🔉<br /><br /></li><li>Team players who thrive in a collaborative environment🪴<br /><br /></li><li>No experience? No problem— we’ll train you from day one📝</li></ul><p><strong>✨✨Take the first step toward a confident, rewarding career.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Apply today and start building your future with us!✨✨</strong></p>",
